🧪 Experiment 10

Question: Design and implement wait mechanisms to handle dynamic web elements using implicit or explicit waits.

Code:

from selenium import webdriver
from selenium.webdriver.common.by import By
from selenium.webdriver.support.ui import WebDriverWait
from selenium.webdriver.support import expected_conditions as EC

driver = webdriver.Chrome()
driver.get("https://google.com")

wait = WebDriverWait(driver,10)
element = wait.until(EC.presence_of_element_located((By.NAME,"q")))

How to Run:

nano exp10.py
python exp10.py

Explanation: Uses explicit wait to handle dynamic elements.
